{"tid":2234581,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男子被控旺角管有攻擊性武器 罪名不成立","createTime":"2020-10-08T04:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T05:57:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"67723d0c0757d00796f6dc46d003e0e7221288d7","tid":2234581,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10099&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5HwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=b1675ea5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10099</a><br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第七庭 <br />\n#張天雁裁判官 <br />\n#審訊<br />\n#1102旺角<br />\n<br />\n譚(29)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：管有攻擊性武器或適合作非法用途的工具<br />\n<br />\n控罪詳情：2019年11月2日在旺角渡船街及奶路臣街交界，管有兩支士巴拿、一支鐵錘及一包膠索帶。<br />\n<br />\n（審訊內容後補）<br />\n<br />\n裁決理由：<br />\n<br />\n本案主要依賴第1控方證人(13840)的口供，張官認為證人在庭上的證據與記事冊及口供紙有關鍵出入，當中包括：當時被告是自己一個還是5至6個集結，亞皆老街上是否有路障<br />\n<br />\n張官將口供紙的紀錄推到最高點，被告只是身穿黑衣且跑向渡船街，但被捕附近沒有非法集結，法庭無法肯定被告管有物品的意圖，再者被告在會面紀錄中提及自己是一名剷車工作員，被告是一名沒有案底的人士，法庭謹記被告的犯罪傾向性偏低，被告可能利用工具作合法或非法用途，法庭無法肯定被告有意圖使用工具作非法用途，環境證供不足以推論到毫無合理疑點，張官最終裁定被告罪名不成立"},{"pid":"60e4d484f6fdea3764d926dc5bb575862f128130","tid":2234581,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc61849482a7b4c72fb74a9e1b832f3ac282e430","tid":2234581,"uid":268153,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:07:44.000Z","msg":"黑警又鳩拉"},{"pid":"bce5926285f10ee4e10c2ff2905dcbe452149aad","tid":2234581,"uid":274680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d821d03eb2bda69675621db901b31e66c0f8deea","tid":2234581,"uid":234589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbb0aa78cbba3b6c2c3645bfcbb49d47b2df2fe","tid":2234581,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:11:37.000Z","msg":"但有單有個女仔後巷搜到有索帶又入到？"},{"pid":"637db0027c0e7ee4a23f5e59ec733db7df75931f","tid":2234581,"uid":45910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9dbb0aa78cbba3b6c2c3645bfcbb49d47b2df2fe","tid":2234581,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:11:37.000Z","msg":"但有單有個女仔後巷搜到有索帶又入到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:12:20.000Z","msg":"裁判官唔同 (好似係)"},{"pid":"ddb3595027c3912d05ce48ff4fcf46acc3e4d23e","tid":2234581,"uid":210682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:12:38.000Z","msg":"好彩遇正常官"},{"pid":"5b6b42ccf774fbd9b202f860b96470c1814a957c","tid":2234581,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d071713c61cad8f1ba74fba6474a4546c5339270","tid":2234581,"uid":78892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6273b3e340f1bef4d20e33ed563a77db3a98aee8","tid":2234581,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc61849482a7b4c72fb74a9e1b832f3ac282e430","tid":2234581,"uid":268153,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:07:44.000Z","msg":"黑警又鳩拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab8fa679f517ea64159bbb6ca23fa6cf546a5cd","tid":2234581,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bce5926285f10ee4e10c2ff2905dcbe452149aad","tid":2234581,"uid":274680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2e0ee1fdc1b1d4a41512ef90ca2e5531aaf075","tid":2234581,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d821d03eb2bda69675621db901b31e66c0f8deea","tid":2234581,"uid":234589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8375c6ac2c1af2e5bde0768e7ce59f61f23e9366","tid":2234581,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dbb0aa78cbba3b6c2c3645bfcbb49d47b2df2fe","tid":2234581,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:11:37.000Z","msg":"但有單有個女仔後巷搜到有索帶又入到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f6e0fa20a8fc8534fc0a26f8346ac359e54945","tid":2234581,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:19:33.000Z","msg":"剷車師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6fc25dba5f962eb170110c1f3397869515e91a","tid":2234581,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:22:13.000Z","msg":"蘇文隆判嘅話就好多推測，然後罪名成立"},{"pid":"0d1ec2023e2668410f99e6a5ca20d0af1814b78b","tid":2234581,"uid":234589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dbb0aa78cbba3b6c2c3645bfcbb49d47b2df2fe","tid":2234581,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:11:37.000Z","msg":"但有單有個女仔後巷搜到有索帶又入到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:23:03.000Z","msg":"睇描述呢單環境證供附近冇非法集結<br />\n<br />\n當佢經過掛"},{"pid":"7758880a0a1b5a92ca1f3221b15b2462ea845ad7","tid":2234581,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:24:41.000Z","msg":"署理主任裁判官<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">張潔宜</span></span>指，警員由截停至制服被告只有 20 至 30 秒，在電光火石之間，未能鉅細無遺形容當中細節，亦不影響可信性。相反，被告供詞不合情理，裁判官質疑當時沒有肺炎，《禁蒙面法》亦生效，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">「點解睇戲要著黑衫同戴口罩？」認為被告裝束與示威者相同，會使警員起疑。裁判官今（8 日）在屯門裁判法院裁定罪名成立，判監禁 4 星期。被告獲准保釋等候上訴。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n官可理解警員供詞不一<br />\n<br />\n署理主任裁判官張潔宜裁決時稱，雖然辯方指警員描述他們與被告之間距離不一致，認為兩名警員證供出現分歧。不過，裁判官認為警員單憑估計、沒有量度實際距離，出現不一致是可以理解。另外辯方庭上播片，稱不見被告有指罵等明顯動作，惟裁判官認為片段不清晰，無法看到被告動作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裁判官指兩名警員由截停至制服被告，只有 20 至 30 秒，在電光火石之間，警員未能在庭上鉅細無遺形容當中細節，亦不影響他們的可信性，遂裁定兩名警員為誠實可靠證人，並接納他們證供。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被告自辯稱當日偕女友看電影，裁判官指被告當時穿著黑衫及黑口罩，但當時沒有肺炎，《禁蒙面法》亦生效，「點解睇戲要著黑衫同戴口罩？」裁判官又指當日有示威者行出馬路指罵警察，被告衣著與示威者相同，會使警方起疑。如果他只是橫過馬路到戲院買票，為何要走向警員方向及走上行車路，認為被告不合情理及不可信。裁判官認為被告當日曾指罵及反抗警員，終裁定罪名成立。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1N70Ypv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1N70Ypv.png&h=ced7e6c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dd4423ee644b5d47cd721c9f9a2fd86517bed69","tid":2234581,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:50:08.000Z","msg":"被告在會面紀錄中提及自己是一名剷車工作員<br />\n<br />\nKey"},{"pid":"eded9d199159cfed813d329a2b7e95316b972f28","tid":2234581,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T05:06:25.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c4d448985f473b0ee51622cc809897ceb43044","tid":2234581,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dbb0aa78cbba3b6c2c3645bfcbb49d47b2df2fe","tid":2234581,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:11:37.000Z","msg":"但有單有個女仔後巷搜到有索帶又入到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T05:17:39.000Z","msg":"我覺得同買六合彩冇分別<br />\n你好彩就冇事<br />\n跟本唔係法律"},{"pid":"7c37fd260231b38c3502f9e74aca024c0ab93c2f","tid":2234581,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T05:26:34.000Z","msg":"DOJ又要上訴了"},{"pid":"be4e89c27d7b9ff34ddfece2a8e9ebbc0300d194","tid":2234581,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":